<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>The Tasha Mellett Foundation</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        color: #000000;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 30px 20px;
      }

      /* HEADER STYLES — center aligned */
      .header {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
        gap: 15px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
      }

      .header img {
        width: 150px;
        height: auto;
        object-fit: contain;
      }

      /* RISING BOX */
      .rising-box {
        background-color: #6a4a3c;
        color: #ffffff;
        padding: 15px 25px;
        margin: 0 auto 20px auto;
        width: fit-content;
        border-radius: 8px;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 18px;
        letter-spacing: 2px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      /* DONATE BUTTON */
      .donate-button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #6a4a3c;
        color: #ffffff !important; /* force white text */
        padding: 12px 25px;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 5px;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 16px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      }

      .donate-button:hover {
        background-color: #4f362c;
      }

      /* CONTENT STYLES */
      .content {
        text-align: center;
        line-height: 1.6;
        font-size: 15px;
        margin-top: 15px;
      }

      .content strong {
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      .subtitle {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #555555;
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: -5px;
      }

      /* SOCIAL LINKS */
      .socials {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 25px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }

      .socials a {
        color: #000000;
        text-decoration: none;
        margin: 0 8px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }

      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 25px;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #555555;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="header">
        <img
          src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dr5yanrd3/image/upload/v1759605202/logoUrl_utmjqo.png"
          alt="The Tasha Mellett Foundation Logo"
        />
        <img
          src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dr5yanrd3/image/upload/v1759605202/potrait_hw4r8b.png"
          alt="Tasha Mellett Portrait"
        />
      </div>

      <h3 class="subtitle">Welcome to The Tasha Mellett Foundation!</h3>
      <p class="subtitle">
        Born From Love. Built For Warriors... Nobody Fights Alone!
      </p>
      <p class="subtitle">Launching on 11/11/25.</p>

      <div class="content">
        <p>
          Our Mission is to change the world by directly helping Warriors on
          their Cancer Journey and we are honored to have you join us…
        </p>

        <p>
          Our guiding principles are
          <strong>Kindness, Compassion and Love.</strong>
        </p>

        <p>
          We’ll keep you updated on all the exciting things to come, but in the
          meantime, please consider making a donation to further our mission.
        </p>

        <a
          href="https://funraise.org/give/The-Tasha-Mellett-Foundation-Inc/b50adf77-3e64-4992-95dc-f61282f8f197"
          class="donate-button"
          target="_blank"
        >
          DONATE NOW
        </a>

        <p>We are incredibly grateful for your support… Nobody fights Alone!</p>

        <p>
          Please follow us on social media for updates and inspiring stories!
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="socials">
        <a href="https://www.tiktok.com/@tashagiving">TIKTOK</a>
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/thetashamellettfoundation"
          >INSTAGRAM</a
        >
        <a href="https://www.facebook.com/thetashamellettfoundation"
          >FACEBOOK</a
        >
      </div>

      <div class="footer">
        &copy; 2025 The Tasha Mellett Foundation. All rights reserved.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
